---
title: Korean Beef Bulgogi-Style Slaw with Asian Slaw, Fried Egg & Soy Mayo
description: This beef bulgogi bowl is dressing to impress anyone who sits at your table. A rainbow slaw tossed with the sweet and smokey
taste of charred sweetcorn holds up the succulent Korean stir-fry sauced beef, wearing nothing less than a creamy soy mayo drizzle. Don’t forget the jewel in the ensemble, the fried egg.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving and under 30g carbohydrates per serving.*
